headline: Henry Schein’s 28th Annual ‘Back to School’ Program Supports Students Worldwide
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., August 19, 2025--For the 28th consecutive year, Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC) is helping students worldwide start the academic year off right through its "Back to School" program, a flagship initiative of Henry Schein Cares, the Company’s global corporate citizenship program. Team Schein Members (TSMs) at 45 locations in the U.S., Canada, Italy, Spain, the U.K., and Ireland are helping more than 5,200 students gain confidence and excitement for the school year.
